query:
insert into route (
              id,
              "from",
              "to",
              nav_mode,
              speed,
              fuel_cost,
              travel_time,
              engine_condition
            )
            SELECT * FROM UNNEST(
              $1::integer[],
              $2::character varying[],
              $3::character varying[],
              $4::character varying[],
              $5::integer[],
              $6::integer[],
              $7::double precision[],
              $8::double precision[]
            )
            on conflict (id) do nothing
